description.text:
After hours of work I had problem with the new extruder from Makerbot. THe spring was not strong as at the beginning --&gt; PLA was not always taken by the extruder.<br />
So I made an adjustable extruder to solve this problem.  
You just need a M4 bolt, a M4 nut and a little spring. All the rest is like &quot;Replicator 2 Drive Block&quot;
